  <original-body>I can't use dom_id in controllers anymore:

@@@ ruby
format.html do
  redirect_to(forum_topic_post_path(@forum, @topic, @post, :anchor =&gt; dom_id(@post)))
end
@@@

All I had to do was manually include `ActionController::RecordIdentifier` into `ActionController::Base`.  That's the easiest fix, but I wonder if this was taken out on purpose since `#dom_id` is primarily used in views.</original-body>
